{
  "id": "reader-survey-2026",
  "title": "2026 Reader Survey",
  "intro": "Once a year I like to stop and ask who's out there, who’s reading, and how I can serve you better. This short check-in directly shapes the future of WTFJHT. About 4–6 minutes, and anonymous unless you add your email at the end.",
  "submit_label": "Submit survey",
  "thanks_title": "Thank you.",
  "thanks_body": "That's it! Thanks for taking the time to share your thoughts.",
  "already_title": "You're all set.",
  "already_body": "Looks like you already filled this out the reader survey. A+, gold star for you. ",
  "anon_optout_label": "Let me answer anonymously instead. ",
  "_note": "SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH (PasteUp). Edit here, then run `npm run publish:survey` in PasteUp/server to push the projected schema to Cloudflare KV (the Worker validates against it) + WTFJHT _data/forms/ (the renderer reads it). Keep option/question `id`s stable after launch (they are the stored data + branch refs); change `label`s freely.",
